# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# long-dev / AI-assisted-development scaffolding (NOT part of the open-source
# platform). These are local-only dev tooling — agent/skill/command/design
# docs, framework state, watcher caches. They are intentionally NOT tracked:
# the open-source release ships the platform only, not the AI-dev scaffolding.
# Cross-machine consistency of these is maintained separately (or treated as
# single-machine); see AGENTS.md / .opencode/skills/long-dev/SKILL.md.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.ai/
.opencode/
AGENTS.md
opencode.json
.claude/

# AI-session fix/summary logs (dev scaffolding, not platform docs)
REVIEW-FIXES.md
docs/SESSION-SUMMARY.md

# 用户 idea 输入 + 处理日志（本地用户文件，不入开源 git）
user_idea.txt
.idea_processed.md

# Pre-scrub git backup (contains old history w/ secrets) — never track
.git.backup-pre-scrub/
